data.description: This property on 303 Berg Ave in Camden, AR is an absolute standout! It has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and they've even added -new roof to it.  With features like a new  hot water heater, attic insulation, and a deck with ceiling fans and lights, it's definitely a property that stands out from the rest.  The interior has been freshly painted in a soft gray, and the kitchen fixtures have been updated too, they've also added a 12x32 tiny home suite with 2 lofts and electricity! It's like having a bonus space for guests
